35
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:51,071
Then tell me.

36
00:02:51,191 --> 00:02:52,191
What's it?

37
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,830
God's Punishment Mountain.

38
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,111
Bitter Hundred Times.

39
00:02:57,830 --> 00:02:58,990
