52
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:39,071
Let me hold you back and rest.

53
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,631
Thank you, Youyue.

54
00:03:43,631 --> 00:03:44,550
In the past,

55
00:03:44,671 --> 00:03:46,550
