118
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,711
But silly child,

119
00:07:01,591 --> 00:07:02,911
in this world,

120
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,870
the only thing I can't let go of

121
00:07:08,550 --> 00:07:09,630
is you.

122
00:07:10,271 --> 00:07:11,151
Regardless of

123
00:07:12,031 --> 00:07:13,750
