174
00:10:37,311 --> 00:10:38,790
Rong,

175
00:10:40,111 --> 00:10:41,390
I loved you so much.

176
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:43,990
All this time,

177
00:10:45,071 --> 00:10:46,910
