449
00:23:16,031 --> 00:23:17,271
but now,

450
00:23:17,870 --> 00:23:18,831
after all the numerous hardships

451
00:23:18,831 --> 00:23:19,870
we've been through,

452
00:23:20,311 --> 00:23:21,710
