492
00:25:15,870 --> 00:25:17,230
You're always brave

493
00:25:17,430 --> 00:25:18,670
and move forward without hesitation.

494
00:25:19,311 --> 00:25:20,791
When you encountered Ge Bin,

495
00:25:20,950 --> 00:25:22,630
